text:
Toxic positivity is a thing. It can be insincere and annoying. 

Toxic negativity is a thing. It can be draining and devastating.

Perhaps, the goal is to be less extreme and less toxic. 

The goal is to rumble in the middle. To be brave and vulnerable, authentic and empathetic.
